#Command Briefing

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("The GTSC Styx, a high-level research vessel, failed to check in three days ago. Its last known position was near a localized subspace instability in the Adhara system.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("You are being deployed as part of Alpha wing to conduct a recon sweep. We need to know if this was a Vasudan strike or something else.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("Use the Loki's advanced sensor suite to scan any surviving cargo or debris. If you encounter hostiles, your priority is to gather data and return to the Erebus. Do not engage unless necessary.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none


